title: Schwartz injured in practice, Rattie recalled
text:
Jaden Schwartz injured in Blues practice, Ty Rattie recalled from minors THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   23, 2015 - 11:45 pmLast Updated: October 23, 2015 - 11:45 pm   
People: 
Missouri (724) 

ST. LOUIS â€” St. Louis Blues forward Jaden Schwartz was injured in practice, and the team recalled forward Ty Rattie from Chicago of the AHL. 
The team said on its website that Schwartz slipped and slid into a goal post. He has four assists in seven games. 
The 22-year-old Rattie has four goals and seven points in three games with the Wolves. He was a second-round pick in 2011.
